data.description: Short Sale. Welcome to your dream home! This single-family gem boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an open floor design with sleek laminate floors throughout, combining contemporary style with practicality. The spacious living room features a decorative fireplace with a stunning stone backdrop, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings.    The kitchen is a chef's haven, equipped with quartz countertops, modern smart-capable appliances, and a central island offering built-in storage and a smart charging hub. The property comes with a robust security system, providing peace of mind for you and your family.    Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood near schools, parks, shopping, and dining, this home is both inviting and practical. Easy access to major transportation routes ensures a seamless commute. Don't miss the chance to turn your homeownership dreams into reality with this exceptional property. Schedule a showing today!
